Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:02:24.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.95,0:00:23.25,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right! Now let's move forward
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.25,0:00:26.67,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,with the sun always in our hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.67,0:00:30.05,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,As power passes through our clasped hands
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.05,0:00:34.34,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,let's grab hold of our wishes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.18,0:00:48.73,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Working together, let's ride the giant waves
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.73,0:00:55.90,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry toward the excitement--\Nthere's the starting signal
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.90,0:01:02.87,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Now's the time to set sail-- let's raise anchor
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.87,0:01:10.00,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut through the rainbow-colored wind\Nand head for a sea of adventure
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.00,0:01:13.51,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be a journey fraught with injury
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.51,0:01:17.34,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,but what you cherish most will be right there
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.34,0:01:21.39,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And if you get into a jam
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.39,0:01:24.39,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll always be there to protect you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.39,0:01:28.65,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right! Now let's move forward
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.65,0:01:32.11,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,with the sun always in our hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.11,0:01:35.36,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If a storm hits, let's put\Nour arms around each other
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.36,0:01:39.62,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and gaze at the light beyond
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.62,0:01:43.33,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If we gather up the pieces of our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.33,0:01:46.62,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,they'll make a map leading to tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.62,0:01:50.04,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,So let's grab hold of our wishes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.04,0:01:55.46,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,under the same flag-- together, we're one
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.46,0:01:57.80,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,One Piece
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.12,0:02:27.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Great Adventure at Long Ring Long Land!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.51,0:02:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's our bearing look, Nami-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.81,0:02:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.89,0:02:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's our Nami-san for ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.40,0:03:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The holes are just about patched up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.66,0:03:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boy, am I glad I had the foresight
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.66,0:03:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to take a bunch of scrap\Nlumber back at that dock!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.00,0:03:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're great, Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.33,0:03:12.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should be okay for a little while now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.88,0:03:19.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It went out!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.92,0:03:21.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Out of fuel?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.84,0:03:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Usopp! We're about\Nto make a splashdown!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.05,0:03:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry, Chopper! Bring all those boards up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.72,0:03:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.35,0:03:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can do it, octopus balloon!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.00,0:03:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot! Just hit the deck!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.61,0:03:41.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.96,0:03:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,J-Just in the nick of time!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.17,0:04:04.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There, you should be all better now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.42,0:04:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's twice you've helped us out now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.01,0:04:10.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.70,0:04:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take care!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.34,0:04:17.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you make some\Ngood friends in the Blue Sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.11,0:04:20.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go give all those Grand Line\Noctopuses a throttling!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.69,0:04:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So long, seafood ingredient!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.13,0:04:24.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.77,0:04:26.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful on your way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.99,0:04:32.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, then...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.95,0:04:36.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Set the sails, men! Let's go to the next island!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.91,0:04:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, hold on, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.04,0:04:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Let us rest a little!\N--Don't forget where we are!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.26,0:04:45.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone could sail these seas\Nif it was okay to be so carefree!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.30,0:04:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you getting at?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.64,0:04:51.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The waves have been looking a little strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.01,0:04:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hop to it, everyone! Turn to port!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.48,0:04:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Nami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.11,0:05:08.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, here it comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.78,0:05:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Full speed ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.45,0:05:14.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--This isn't good!\N--There's stuff in the wave, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.08,0:05:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Those are Sea Monkeys!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.76,0:05:25.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's all the ruckus here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.17,0:05:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.01,0:05:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit pushing! W-We gotta stay away from 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.60,0:05:31.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're having a falling out?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.99,0:05:47.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Bellamy!\N--Sarquiss!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.32,0:05:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please! Make him stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.78,0:05:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please! Stop! Why are you doing this...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.25,0:05:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What's happening?!\N--Sarquiss is in pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.39,0:06:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Why, you ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.94,0:06:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sarquiss... Bellamy...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.51,0:06:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because you've tarnished\Nthis symbol of mine, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.60,0:06:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Does the sky island exist or not?"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.79,0:06:21.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Is the city of gold real or not?"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.40,0:06:26.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't give a care about any of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.73,0:06:29.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're to twist people around by\Ntaking advantage of differing opinions.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.87,0:06:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I told you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.74,0:06:34.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...wasn't it, Bellamy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.74,0:06:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's... Don Quixote Doflamingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.85,0:06:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's one of the Seven Warlords of the Sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.92,0:06:44.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He used to have a bounty over 300 million!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.38,0:06:46.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's a guy like him doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.42,0:06:51.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need useless punks\Nlike you serving under me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.37,0:06:54.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap! My body's moving on its own!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.85,0:06:57.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! Please, don't...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.10,0:07:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.36,0:07:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellamy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.11,0:07:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G-Give me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.95,0:07:16.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me one more chance...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.83,0:07:20.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-- we-- will follow you loyally!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.75,0:07:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Bellamy!\N--No more, Bellamy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.63,0:07:29.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I lost, but I never went\Nagainst your principles!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.47,0:07:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I swear on your symbol!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.26,0:07:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is just my way of doing things!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.76,0:07:36.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We couldn't just run 'im off;
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.26,0:07:39.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he would've reached you someday!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.70,0:07:44.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How very touching,\Nobedient subordinate of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.36,0:07:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I like about you, Bellamy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.44,0:07:55.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A "New Era" is just around\Nthe corner. Do as you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.03,0:08:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... I don't need you anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.28,0:08:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doflamingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.13,0:08:15.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He took out the notorious Bellamy--\Na rookie worth 55 million--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.47,0:08:17.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,like he was a baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.76,0:08:20.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's finally beginning!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.68,0:08:22.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better get ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.18,0:08:26.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A world where only true pirates\Ncan survive is drawing near!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.02,0:08:29.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those of you who are powerless--\Nrun for your lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.47,0:08:31.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soon, the tide of the times will wash over all
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.48,0:08:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and a new era of champions will be upon us!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.88,0:08:59.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Things've sure calmed down...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.72,0:09:01.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't lower our guard yet, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.92,0:09:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Emergency report! Emergency report!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.78,0:09:06.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ship spotted at 12 o'clock!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.85,0:09:09.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Huh? Are they bad guys?!\N--This is the worst possible time!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.90,0:09:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, there's no flag or sails!\NI don't know what kind of ship it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.40,0:09:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, nothing at all?!\NWhat are they on the sea for, then?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.95,0:09:21.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heck if I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.62,0:09:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The crew seems unusually small, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.24,0:09:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.78,0:09:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're looking really timid!\NAlmost like they're lifeless!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.43,0:09:39.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sea Monkeys! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.82,0:09:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Again?!\N--They followed us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.01,0:09:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Crap! There's no wind!\N--Hurry! Furl the sails!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.60,0:09:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Row! Row!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.40,0:09:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the...?! Is that ship gonna be all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.69,0:09:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The wave's gonna swallow 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.24,0:09:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! You guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.66,0:10:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A giant wave and monkeys are coming! Turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.37,0:10:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Oh!\N--Whoa! A ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.16,0:10:07.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A pirate ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.62,0:10:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Men! Get up! An enemy ship!\NLet's swipe their treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.68,0:10:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! A giant wave's coming!\NWe gotta escape first!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.58,0:10:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--We can't let that ship get away!\N--Ready the cannons!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.20,0:10:19.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who made you boss?! You do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.19,0:10:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn! Someone turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.39,0:10:23.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What an unorganized ship...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.72,0:10:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget 'em. They're not on our side.\NThey wanna steal our treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.38,0:10:29.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Which way do we turn?!\N--How should I know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.48,0:10:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Someone, give orders! Navigator!\N--Don't got one!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.04,0:10:35.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Captain!\N--Don't got one!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.49,0:10:40.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who just fired that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.70,0:10:42.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grrr!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.53,0:10:46.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--It's no use! It's gonna swallow us!\N--Damn! You're all incompetent!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.92,0:10:51.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--You're one to talk!\N--We can't handle a single wave?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.24,0:11:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, it's one thing after another...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.95,0:11:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's finally calmed down.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.57,0:11:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those waves were actually\Nthe Sea Monkeys' doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.95,0:11:37.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The humidity and temperature\Nare pretty stable now,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.71,0:11:40.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so we must already be in\Nthe next island's climate zone!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.11,0:11:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Robin. See anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.93,0:11:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An island's been visible for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.35,0:11:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why couldn't you say so sooner?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.35,0:11:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're such a wet blanket!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.89,0:11:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen! Whenever you see an island, say this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.77,0:11:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.02,0:11:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Men! I see an island! Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.15,0:12:01.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.40,0:12:04.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--The fog is rather thick.\N--You're ignoring me again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.82,0:12:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fog? We gotta be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.70,0:12:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Chopper! Keep forward watch!\N--Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.04,0:12:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Do you know how much we've\Nbeen waiting to see an island?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.92,0:12:16.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. I'll be more mindful.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.85,0:12:19.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? In that case, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.46,0:12:23.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, is anyone else curious\Nabout that ship from earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.13,0:12:25.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They said they had no captain or navigator,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.09,0:12:28.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and they didn't even have flags,\Nsails, motivation, or organization...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.72,0:12:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of pirates\Nwould go around like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.98,0:12:34.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably got into a battle and lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.19,0:12:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And their captain died\Nand they got plundered...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.48,0:12:40.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that can't be it!\NI got a good look at their ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.94,0:12:43.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There weren't any signs of a battle at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.19,0:12:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet the ship was completely bare of\Nall the essentials that pirates need!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.82,0:12:51.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So they weren't pirates, then.\NDon't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.75,0:12:56.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But they sure seemed like pirates to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.96,0:12:59.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I somehow get a bad feeling about this...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.29,0:13:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You always do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.55,0:13:03.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! I wonder if there's a town!\NI hope they have a shipyard!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.72,0:13:06.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy! Don't go jumping off right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.47,0:13:14.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope we'll get a good shipwright to join us!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.02,0:13:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're near the shore! Get the anchor ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.11,0:13:21.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, guys... Listen to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.11,0:13:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper! Usopp's got the\N"Can't Go On the Island" disease!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.63,0:13:27.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no cure for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.36,0:13:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.41,0:13:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.79,0:13:40.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.25,0:13:43.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this place?! So cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.01,0:13:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all grass as far as I can see!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.97,0:13:51.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, what a dull place.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.55,0:13:53.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you suppose anyone lives here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.72,0:13:55.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Yahoo!\N--Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.93,0:13:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.36,0:14:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh. They barge right into\Nuncharted territory like it's nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.90,0:14:10.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With a view like this,\Nit's clear there's no danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.00,0:14:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Chopper--?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.81,0:14:28.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A human?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.47,0:14:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No human's this fluffy and shaggy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.55,0:14:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a bear!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.31,0:14:39.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! So long! A long bear!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.28,0:14:40.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So high up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.77,0:14:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! This is an apple! It's so long!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.52,0:14:49.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Don't eat it!\N--Yum!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.53,0:14:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the other trees are crazy tall too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.04,0:15:01.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look! Is that a house?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.75,0:15:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it looks like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.59,0:15:08.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's check it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.35,0:15:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your relative!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.60,0:15:18.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a deer! I'm a reindeer!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.91,0:15:36.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shake!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.49,0:15:39.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Watch this, Chopper!\N--Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.21,0:15:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! You're awesome, Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.54,0:15:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.67,0:15:50.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beg!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.05,0:15:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So long!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.97,0:16:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I can't even see its head!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.74,0:16:12.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where'd they run off to?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.45,0:16:14.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were rolling around just a minute ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.41,0:16:17.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should disembark too.\NThere could be food here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.58,0:16:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Robin-chan! We're getting off the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.79,0:16:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.12,0:16:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, talk about long...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.88,0:16:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is everything here so loong?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.01,0:16:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like just looking at them's\Ngonna make me looong too...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.30,0:16:40.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just what kind of island is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.93,0:16:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi! We're coming in!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.20,0:16:44.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.85,0:16:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hold on, Luffy! I bet this is\Nwhere the boss of the island lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.66,0:16:52.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's gonna be some horrifyingly long\Nsnake-man monster! I just know it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.86,0:16:54.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.28,0:16:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Luffy! Usopp! I found a giraffe!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.66,0:17:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.75,0:17:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That ain't a giraffe...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.88,0:17:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's got a long neck,\Nbut it's a horse. A long-horse...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.80,0:17:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a horse?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.34,0:17:17.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a pretty horse!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.68,0:17:20.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's a girl! She says her name is Shelly!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.22,0:17:24.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This saddle must mean\Nsomeone's here after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.56,0:17:26.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up, Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.65,0:17:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.94,0:17:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--See those two bamboo trees?\N--Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.61,0:17:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! I can't see their tops! Talk about long!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.16,0:17:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a closer look...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.95,0:17:40.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.91,0:17:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're running away!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.00,0:17:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha...?! This must be another long animal!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.17,0:17:49.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The bamboo tree's attacking Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.84,0:17:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey! You all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.30,0:17:54.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let you beat me, bamboo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.42,0:17:55.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Careful, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.97,0:18:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum Whip!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.68,0:18:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! You beat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.66,0:18:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! I cut it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.21,0:18:11.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's your owner?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.73,0:18:16.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know? That sounds lonely...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.03,0:18:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It could be bad guys! Stay there and hide!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.08,0:18:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.62,0:18:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.00,0:18:35.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I cut a bamboo tree and a spirit appeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.50,0:18:50.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our ship's... been blocked from leaving?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.98,0:18:52.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are they planning?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.02,0:18:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the ship I saw earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.90,0:18:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you guys?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.36,0:19:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's a fight you want, get down here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.03,0:19:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are the Foxy Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.70,0:19:07.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be hasty! All we want... is a showdown!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.33,0:19:11.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A spirit?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.54,0:19:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. He appeared after I cut the bamboo tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.42,0:19:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey. Say something, you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.17,0:19:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I remember you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.22,0:19:25.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a long time. How are you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.47,0:19:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One of you knows him?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.85,0:19:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Nope.\N--Me neither...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.18,0:19:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, no wonder I didn't recognize you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.65,0:19:35.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, what a flake! Who are you, old guy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.44,0:19:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Tonjit. You have my thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.48,0:19:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I assume you're the ones\Nwho knocked me off my stilts?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.41,0:19:48.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stilts?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.87,0:19:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! They are!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.71,0:19:57.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But they were so long,\Nwe couldn't see the top at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.38,0:20:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed. I was at the very top!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.92,0:20:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so you're not a spirit that came\Nout because I cut a bamboo tree,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.01,0:20:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you're an old guy who fell\N'cause his stilts broke?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.52,0:20:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why were you on such long stilts anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.60,0:20:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always been fond of stilts,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.27,0:20:21.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I tried to make the world's longest\Nstilts using this island's bamboo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.19,0:20:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I managed to get on them, but then\NI was too scared to come back down!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.03,0:20:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're crazy, old guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.53,0:20:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was up there... for ten years!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.87,0:20:31.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're really crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.29,0:20:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were on stilts for ten whole years?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.08,0:20:38.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. The bamboo continued\Nto grow the entire time, too,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.75,0:20:42.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,making it even harder\Nfor me to come back down...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.04,0:20:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So scary...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.18,0:20:47.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's your only comment after ten years?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.51,0:20:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are many trees on this island\Njust as tall as the stilts, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.72,0:20:54.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was able to survive on fruit I could find.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.81,0:20:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He talks about it so casually.\NEspecially being up there for so long...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.77,0:21:00.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of long...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.52,0:21:04.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is everything on this\Nisland so long, old guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.36,0:21:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It might seem that way to an outsider,\Nbut there is a reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.41,0:21:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As you can see, a giant,\Ngrassy plain covers this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.62,0:21:15.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In short, everything here is long\Ndue to a longing for excitement.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.54,0:21:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa. He went and said it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.38,0:21:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Over there, for example...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.17,0:21:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--...is a plaaatypus.\N--You just said it longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.51,0:21:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a Daaachshund.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.43,0:21:30.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Are you that same dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.22,0:21:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still passing by?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.35,0:21:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful-- there are ferocious animals too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.77,0:21:40.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See? That's a snow leooopard.\NDon't let it bite you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.06,0:21:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leopard?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.27,0:21:44.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is it only long sideways?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.75,0:22:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There he is...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.13,0:22:05.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.11,0:22:23.23,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,A piece of a dream that we started grasping
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.23,0:22:26.78,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Chasing after something constant
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.78,0:22:31.41,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We send our aspirations sailing into the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.37,0:22:34.66,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Even when we're exhausted
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.66,0:22:37.83,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We have a compass that can\Nsearch for something constant
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.83,0:22:43.25,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, do you think we can keep it forever?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.25,0:22:46.17,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,At the end of the dream\Nthat we will reach someday
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.17,0:22:48.97,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We want to be adults as we\Nare now as much as possible
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.97,0:22:51.93,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We pray to this endless sky that we look up at
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.93,0:22:55.01,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Eternally... Eternally...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.01,0:22:57.81,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Wild fantasies from our childhood
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.81,0:23:00.64,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We trace unforgettable memories
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.64,0:23:06.32,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And try to keep the embers\Nburning that still consume us
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.32,0:23:09.11,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,To this familiar sunny sky
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.11,0:23:11.95,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Together we entrust our feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.95,0:23:14.53,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We go beyond the changing time
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.53,0:23:17.33,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Eternally... Eternally...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.55,0:23:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Foxy! I take whatever I want!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.80,0:23:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not another weirdo!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.80,0:23:33.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I challenge you, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.64,0:23:36.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Stop talking crazy, Split-Head!\N--"Split-Head"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.56,0:23:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it on! I'll fight you all you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.52,0:23:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Luffy! Don't agree to his game!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.19,0:23:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.44,0:23:45.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"A Davy Back with the Foxy Pirates!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.73,0:23:47.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.15,0:23:50.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.15,0:23:52.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
